00:00:35.390 --> 00:00:38.590
Malignant individuals and groups
use various methods

00:00:38.590 --> 00:00:41.260
to try and force their targets into submission.

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:45.940
Each method attempts to induce its own distinctive psychological deterrent.

00:00:45.940 --> 00:00:48.000
Some try to arouse shame.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:51.800
Others try to instil a sense of helplessness
and dependence.

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:55.020
Others are designed to create intense confusion.

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:57.760
But the aim is always the same:

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:02.940
to train targets to doubt their own judgement
and stop them thinking for themselves.

00:01:02.940 --> 00:01:06.180
Manipulators can then gradually
impose their rules —

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:11.940
rules they can change any time they like
which the target will come to accept without question.

00:01:11.940 --> 00:01:14.440
Manipulators can also isolate the target

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:17.180
away from the people who could help them escape.

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:22.440
Targets are taught to despise or even fear these potential sources of support

00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:24.840
leaving them truly cut off.

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:27.460
In healthy families, as they develop

00:01:27.460 --> 00:01:30.780
infants learn to take progressively larger steps.

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:34.520
They risk longer unaccompanied
explorations of their world

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:36.580
where they encounter some nice things

00:01:36.580 --> 00:01:38.760
and some not-so-nice things.

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:43.080
Secure in the knowledge they can return to safety if they feel overwhelmed

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:44.980
they learn to cope with the bad

00:01:44.980 --> 00:01:46.600
and enjoy the good.

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:51.040
Their self-reliance increases and their world expands.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:53.549
Targets of manipulative groups experience

00:01:53.549 --> 00:01:56.260
this developmental process in reverse.

00:01:56.260 --> 00:01:58.380
They learn to take smaller steps.

00:01:58.380 --> 00:02:01.400
They’re discouraged from engaging with the
outside world

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:04.560
which is portrayed as hostile and dangerous.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:08.120
They’re taught that good only exists within the group.

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:13.040
Their self-reliance decreases and their world shrinks.

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:16.580
Piece by piece, they surrender their autonomy

00:02:16.580 --> 00:02:19.320
and succumb to increasing supervision.

00:02:19.320 --> 00:02:23.420
When faced with dilemmas, they learn
not to trust their own reasoning

00:02:23.420 --> 00:02:27.920
but to seek advice, direction and permission from the group.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:29.780
They’ll be instructed to do things

00:02:29.780 --> 00:02:34.000
that arouse great anxiety and distress,
even heartbreak

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.820
like demonising good people

00:02:35.820 --> 00:02:38.940
and shunning loved ones who disagree with the group.

00:02:38.940 --> 00:02:41.329
They’ll be told they need to be ‘brave’

00:02:41.329 --> 00:02:44.400
