an elder of the abuse

00:32:47.560 --> 00:32:49.320
but was accused of lying

00:32:49.320 --> 00:32:53.000
even though they had access
to his previous confession of abuse.

00:32:53.000 --> 00:32:57.640
Eventually she told the elders unless they
did something, she’d call the police.

00:32:57.640 --> 00:32:59.750
In the following police investigation

00:32:59.750 --> 00:33:04.000
Alison learned of her sister’s abuse and
her father’s confession.

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:06.080
The Panorama report noted:

00:33:06.080 --> 00:33:10.580
‘When he confessed to congregation elders,
Cousins got a mild rebuke.’

00:33:10.580 --> 00:33:14.500
‘When he confessed in court, he got five years in jail.’

00:33:14.500 --> 00:33:17.980
In 2015, another abused individual explained

00:33:17.980 --> 00:33:23.680
how the organisation rationalises its rejection
of secular authorities in abuse cases.

00:33:23.680 --> 00:33:25.140
Testifying anonymously

00:33:25.140 --> 00:33:30.360
to the Australian Royal Commission into
Institutional Responses to Child Sexual Abuse

00:33:30.360 --> 00:33:34.080
she recounted being threatened with
disfellowshipping if she called the police

00:33:34.080 --> 00:33:38.340
by an elder who quoted 1 Corinthians 6: verses 1-8

00:33:38.340 --> 00:33:41.010
which forbids taking brothers to court.

00:33:41.010 --> 00:33:47.669
The Commission heard evidence that the organisation
had kept records of 1,006 alleged abusers

00:33:47.669 --> 00:33:52.420
in Australia since 1950
—&nbsp;none of them reported to police.

00:33:52.420 --> 00:33:57.520
I’ll be exploring the Royal Commission’s
investigation in a future video.

00:33:57.520 --> 00:34:01.620
Apparently this scriptural justification
doesn’t extend to all crime.

00:34:01.620 --> 00:34:06.780
In 2016, a letter to the elders regarding
their ‘Kingdom Halls’

00:34:06.780 --> 00:34:08.580
— their places of worship —

00:34:08.580 --> 00:34:13.600
stated that theft and vandalism should be
promptly reported to the local authorities.

00:34:13.600 --> 00:34:21.300
It explains: ‘When property damage occurs quick
action can go far in preventing further damage’.

00:34:21.300 --> 00:34:25.240
Is that sentiment any less true
of damage to children?

00:34:25.240 --> 00:34:29.140
Are children less important than property?

00:34:29.140 --> 00:34:34.120
By its actions, the organisation reveals its true values.

00:34:34.120 --> 00:34:38.440
Jehovah’s Witness literature repeatedly plays
on wolf and sheep imagery

00:34:38.440 --> 00:34:43.580
comparing non-Witnesses and ex-Witnesses
to oppressive wicked wolves

00:34:43.580 --> 00:34:47.920
intent on attacking a pure and vulnerable flock.

00:34:47.920 --> 00:34:52.040
In reality, the doctrines
of the Jehovah’s Witness leadership

00:34:52.040 --> 00:34:55.820
systematically protect the wolves
inside the organisation

00:34:55.820 --> 00:34:59.660
while forcing the sheep out of the flock.

00:34:59.660 --> 00:35:04.220
Is it plausible that a benevolent
super-intelligent divine being

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:08.160
would create such an glaringly flawed system?

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:15.760
Or does this ugly mess have distinctly
human fingerprints all over it?

00:35:15.760 --> 00:35:18.980
It’s disorientating enough when survivors of child abuse

00:35:18.980 --> 00:35:22.740
get shunned by an organisation
that claims to champion children.

00:35:22.740 --> 00:35:25.080
But they’re hit by another curveball

00:35:25.080 --> 00:35:29.980
when the organisation’s representatives
refuse to admit that it practices shunning.

00:35:29.980 --> 00:35:33.640
Whether it’s in news interviews,
in door-to-door preaching

00:35:33.650 --> 00:35:36.980
or in court hearings under divine oath

00:35:36.980 --> 00:35:38.900
when the subject of shunning comes up

00:35:38.900 --> 00:35:42.000
Witnesses repeatedly go into cover-up mode.

00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:44.720
Suddenly this strictly enforced doctrine

00:35:44.720 --> 00:35:48.260
gets misrepresented
as a matter of personal choice.

00:35:48.260 --> 00:35:50.780
Some witnesses even play the prejudice card

00:35:50.780 --> 00:35:55.580
complaining that the term shunning
evokes unwelcome stereotypes.

00:35:55.580 --> 00:36:01.780
The organisation’s subterfuge regarding
shunning extends to its website —&nbsp;jw.org.

00:36:01.780 --> 00:36:07.380
In its FAQ article ‘Do Jehovah’s Witnesses Shun
Former Members of Their Religion?’

00:36:07.380 --> 00:36:10.360
it even dodges its own question.

00:36:10.360 --> 00:36:13.080
The article says baptised Witnesses who’ve
drifted away

00:36:13.089 --> 00:36:16.240
or no longer preach are not shunned.

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:18.960
This is a misleading example.

00:36:18.960 --> 00:36:22.640
The organisation doesn’t classify these
individuals as former members.

00:36:22.640 --> 00:36:25.840
They’re called ‘inactive’ members
—&nbsp;or ‘faders’.

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:31.040
To become former members they’d have to
disassociate or get disfellowshipped.

00:36:31.040 --> 00:36:33.240
Then they would be shunned.

00:36:33.240 --> 00:36:35.860
The article claims if a man’s disfellowshipped

00:36:35.869 --> 00:36:38.640
and his wife and children are Jehovah’s
Witnesses

00:36:38.640 --> 00:36:41.720
normal family affections and dealings continue.

00:36:41.720 --> 00:36:44.540
This is another misleading example.

00:36:44.540 --> 00:36:48.279
Relatives living in the same household are
considered a special case

00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:51.920
in that the organisation allows
a degree of association.

00:36:51.920 --> 00:36:54.140
What the article neglects to mention

00:36:54.140 --> 00:36:57.740
is that if disfellowshipped family members
ever move out of the house

00:36:57.740 --> 00:37:03.040
barring necessary family business,
they can be shunned like any stranger.

00:37:03.040 --> 00:37:06.500
As the organisation comments with apparent relish:

00:37:06.500 --> 00:37:08.960
if the disfellowshipped or disassociated one

00:37:08.960 --> 00:37:12.600
is a relative living outside the immediate
family circle and home

00:37:12.600 --> 00:37:17.780
it might be possible to have almost no contact
at all with the relative.

00:37:17.780 --> 00:37:23.700
The truth is Witnesses are told to avoid
all normal contact with disfellowshipped relatives

00:37:23.700 --> 00:37:26.240
— including text messages and emails —

00:37:26.240 --> 00:37:29.840
and not to look for excuses
to associate with them.

00:37:29.840 --> 00:37:32.789
Witnesses who maintain unnecessary association

00:37:32.789 --> 00:37:37.280
with disfellowshipped relatives
can be disfellowshipped themselves.

00:37:37.280 --> 00:37:40.900
How does an organisation
that claims to represent ‘the Truth’

00:37:40.900 --> 00:37:46.580
justify its deliberate use of deception to
conceal the sexual abuse of children

00:37:46.580 --> 00:37:51.700
and the doctrine of shunning to which many
of those abused children are then subjected?

00:37:51.700 --> 00:37:55.280
Jehovah’s Witness literature
claims ‘all lying is bad’

00:37:55.280 --> 00:38:00.180
and quotes Biblical passages denouncing lies
as detestable to Jehovah.

00:38:00.180 --> 00:38:05.380
But like David Berg, the organisation gives
itself licence to deceive.

00:38:05.380 --> 00:38:08.860
Just as Berg had his ‘deceivers yet true’ doctrine

00:38:08.860 --> 00:38:11.940
the Jehovah’s Witness Governing Body has
its own version

00:38:11.940 --> 00:38:16.440
called ‘theocratic war strategy’
or ‘theocratic warfare’.

00:38:16.440 --> 00:38:21.080
Like Berg’s doctrine, it strictly forbids
lying to fellow members.

00:38:21.080 --> 00:38:25.820
Like Berg’s doctrine, it denounces lying
for selfish motives.

00:38:25.820 --> 00:38:31.640
And like Berg’s doctrine, it asserts that
non-members are not entitled to the truth.

00:38:31.640 --> 00:38:36.660
Putting these two groups side by side highlights
the perversity of these doctrines.

00:38:36.660 --> 00:38:41.140
Here we have two groups who would each accuse
the other of false teaching

00:38:41.140 --> 00:38:44.320
but wouldn’t consider them entitled to know
the truth.

00:38:44.320 --> 00:38:47.340
Both groups claim their own brand
of deception is fine

00:38:47.340 --> 00:38:49.580
while the other group’s is wicked.

00:38:49.580 --> 00:38:51.540
They’re mirror images

00:38:51.540 --> 00:38:55.900
each accusing the other while exonerating themselves.

00:38:55.900 --> 00:39:02.180
This is the absurdity that results from the hypocritical systems of supremacist groups

00:39:02.180 --> 00:39:06.400
who judge others on standards
they themselves decline to follow.

00:39:06.400 --> 00:39:08.270
The Governing Body of Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:39:08.270 --> 00:39:12.760
claims deception is only used
to prevent harm or persecution.

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:18.480
But does covering up child sexual abuse qualify as preventing harm or persecution?

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:22.460
The problem becomes clear when we
bring back the Catholic Church.

00:39:22.460 --> 00:39:27.600
If the Governing Body wants to defend its cover-up
on the grounds of preventing harm or persecution

00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:31.760
it has to accept the same defence from the
Catholic Church over its cover-up.

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:35.940
More to the point, if it rejects that defence
from the Catholic Church

00:39:35.940 --> 00:39:39.040
it has no defence itself.

00:39:39.040 --> 00:39:41.740
Another hypocrisy regarding the Catholics

00:39:41.749 --> 00:39:45.769
concerns the guilt trip
Jehovah’s Witness elders repeatedly use

00:39:45.769 --> 00:39:49.360
to stop children
reporting their abuse to the authorities.

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:53.180
Children are told they’ll bring reproach
on Jehovah’s name.

00:39:53.180 --> 00:39:56.680
But in its many criticisms regarding
Catholic child abuse

00:39:56.680 --> 00:39:59.520
did the Governing Body reproach their god?

00:39:59.520 --> 00:40:06.460
No. It reproached the church, the pope, the clergy
— the humans who allowed it.

00:40:06.460 --> 00:40:10.720
Likewise, when cases of child abuse
by Jehovah’s Witnesses emerge

00:40:10.720 --> 00:40:12.640
no one’s reproaching Jehovah.

00:40:12.640 --> 00:40:20.520
They’re reproaching the organisation, the Governing Body, the elders —&nbsp;the humans who allow it.

00:40:20.520 --> 00:40:23.200
Telling children they’ll bring reproach on Jehovah

00:40:23.200 --> 00:40:26.080
isn’t just emotionally abusive.

00:40:26.080 --> 00:40:27.720
It’s a lie.

00:40:27.720 --> 00:40:33.760
The organisation’s cover-up regarding shunning also fails to qualify as preventing harm or persecution.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:37.420
It does put the organisation in a very unattractive light.

00:40:37.420 --> 00:40:40.120
But it’s an accurate light.

00:40:40.120 --> 00:40:41.540
The abusive nature of shunning

00:40:41.540 --> 00:40:45.420
is something the organisation itself
unwittingly acknowledged

00:40:45.420 --> 00:40:49.720
in a 2013 Awake! article about the silent treatment.

00:40:49.720 --> 00:40:53.760
It noted with disapproval how some people
use the silent treatment

00:40:53.760 --> 00:40:57.580
to punish or to manipulate others into compliance.

00:40:57.580 --> 00:41:02.100
It even asked readers if that was really how
they want to treat people they love.

00:41:02.100 --> 00:41:07.220
That question can be thrown right back at
the Governing Body in regards to shunning.

00:41:07.220 --> 00:41:13.640
The Jehovah’s Witness organisation
is a group wrestling with huge internal contradictions

00:41:13.640 --> 00:41:20.229
wanting to project a pure, morally clean image
to an outside world it despises

00:41:20.229 --> 00:41:24.839
and in the process, neglecting and abusing
its own members

00:41:25.000 --> 00:41:27.980
in the most callous, heartless ways.

00:41:39.340 --> 00:41:46.300
The Biblical passage Matthew 7:16, says:
‘By their fruits you will recognise them.’

00:41:46.300 --> 00:41:48.200
The Jehovah’s Witness leadership claims

00:41:48.200 --> 00:41:54.180
that its organisation’s authenticity
can be recognised by its fruits.

00:41:54.180 --> 00:41:58.780
It asserts that any religion
unable to unite its devotees

00:41:58.780 --> 00:42:01.840
cannot have the key for uniting humankind.

00:42:01.840 --> 00:42:05.040
And it claims that the fruits of peace and harmony

00:42:05.040 --> 00:42:07.720
found within its organisation

00:42:07.720 --> 00:42:09.920
is proof that it has that key.

00:42:09.920 --> 00:42:14.260
Any group that routinely expels
individuals who criticise or challenge it

00:42:14.260 --> 00:42:19.200
will eventually be left with a pool of uncritical, compliant followers.

00:42:19.200 --> 00:42:22.540
That isn’t the same as ‘uniting your devotees’.

00:42:22.540 --> 00:42:27.660
To unite means to bring together
—&nbsp;to eradicate divisions.

00:42:27.660 --> 00:42:32.340
Eradicating people, as the Jehovah’s Witness
organisation does

00:42:32.340 --> 00:42:35.600
only proves its inability to unite them.

00:42:35.600 --> 00:42:38.760
Silence does not imply peace and harmony.

00:42:38.760 --> 00:42:41.540
Silence can be pregnant with anguish.

00:42:41.540 --> 00:42:46.900
For children whose desperate reports of abuse
are repeatedly dismissed as lies

00:42:46.900 --> 00:42:49.620
and who are threatened with expulsion

00:42:49.620 --> 00:42:53.620
for the sin of tainting their religion’s
false image of pureness

00:42:53.620 --> 00:42:56.100
there is no peace or harmony.

00:42:56.100 --> 00:42:58.800
David Berg and the Jehovah’s Witness leadership

00:42:58.800 --> 00:43:01.600
had opposing views on sex with children.

00:43:01.600 --> 00:43:04.900
But both groups became a sanctuary for molesters.

00:43:04.900 --> 00:43:08.660
In Berg’s case, his doctrines
actively condoned abuse.

00:43:08.660 --> 00:43:13.000
In the case of the Jehovah’s Witness leadership,
even though it denounces abuse

00:43:13.000 --> 00:43:16.719
its maladaptive doctrines work to perpetuate it

00:43:16.719 --> 00:43:20.539
by silencing abused individuals
and their advocates

00:43:20.540 --> 00:43:24.760
and teaching smart abusers that by simply
uttering an apology

00:43:24.760 --> 00:43:28.320
they can avoid all consequences
and continue their molesting.

00:43:28.320 --> 00:43:34.420
In any healthy group, dangerously flawed procedures
are acknowledged and urgently corrected.

00:43:34.420 --> 00:43:41.900
But in groups that claim timeless divine authority
flaws are preserved in the formaldehyde of faith.

00:43:41.900 --> 00:43:44.509
Many individuals abused in dogmatic groups

00:43:44.509 --> 00:43:48.559
like Berg’s Family and the
Jehovah’s Witness organisation

00:43:48.560 --> 00:43:53.540
have been amazed at the warmth, care and support
they’ve received from the outside world

00:43:53.540 --> 00:43:56.760
— a world whose inhabitants they’d been
taught to demonise.

00:43:56.760 --> 00:44:01.200
It’s an eye-opening contrast to the cold,
defensive, often accusing treatment

00:44:01.209 --> 00:44:03.920
they received in their former group.

00:44:03.920 --> 00:44:08.280
By their fruits, we will recognise
the true natures of groups.

00:44:08.280 --> 00:44:12.900
The genuinely benevolent ones
won’t be found concealing abuse.

